name: CryptoSerpent #004
description: Elliott Schwartzer is a former convict who served sentence on Planet Serpy for killing his dentist, accusing him that he was extracting poison from him without consent to make a drug known as Serpentamine. He escaped from his planet in the police ship L-101 with a group of inmates. He lost an eye in a battle with a swordfish. It is said that his best friend Jim Eatsalot came to his rescue.
